#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.iscomplex.iscomplex:1 of
msgid "Returns a bool tensor, where True if input element is complex."
msgstr "返回一个布尔张量，如果输入元素是复数则为 True。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.iscomplex.iscomplex:3 of
msgid ""
"What is tested is whether the input has a non-zero imaginary part, not if"
" the input type is complex."
msgstr "测试的是输入是否具有非零虚部，而不是输入类型是否为复数。"

